public class VAnnotation_Type
extends org.apache.uima.jcas.tcas.Annotation_Type
A UIMA annotation that includes the display value and the original content value. Both are convienence features that will enable one to work directly with the annotation class rather than have to compute them. Updated by JCasGen Thu Aug 18 18:15:19 EDT 2022
